{"tha-ap534:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap534:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap534:0.3":"Vakkalittheraapadana ","tha-ap534:1.1":"“Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap534:1.2":"kappe uppajji nayako; ","tha-ap534:1.3":"Anomanamo amito, ","tha-ap534:1.4":"namena padumuttaro. ","tha-ap534:2.1":"Padumakaravadano, ","tha-ap534:2.2":"padumamalasucchavi; ","tha-ap534:2.3":"Lokenanupalittova, ","tha-ap534:2.4":"toyena padumam yatha. ","tha-ap534:3.1":"Viro padumapattakkho, ","tha-ap534:3.2":"kanto ca padumam yatha; ","tha-ap534:3.3":"Padumuttaragandhova, ","tha-ap534:3.4":"tasma so padumuttaro. ","tha-ap534:4.1":"Lokajettho ca nimmano, ","tha-ap534:4.2":"andhanam nayanupamo; ","tha-ap534:4.3":"Santaveso gunanidhi, ","tha-ap534:4.4":"karunamatisagaro. ","tha-ap534:5.1":"Sa kadaci mahaviro, ","tha-ap534:5.2":"brahmasurasuraccito; ","tha-ap534:5.3":"Sadevamanujakinne, ","tha-ap534:5.4":"janamajjhe jinuttamo. ","tha-ap534:6.1":"Vadanena sugandhena, ","tha-ap534:6.2":"madhurena rutena ca; ","tha-ap534:6.3":"Ranjayam parisam sabbam, ","tha-ap534:6.4":"santhavi savakam sakam. ","tha-ap534:7.1":"Saddhadhimutto sumati, ","tha-ap534:7.2":"mama dassanalalaso; ","tha-ap534:7.3":"Natthi etadiso anno, ","tha-ap534:7.4":"yathayam bhikkhu vakkali. ","tha-ap534:8.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap534:8.2":"nagare brahmanatrajo; ","tha-ap534:8.3":"Hutva sutva ca tam vakyam, ","tha-ap534:8.4":"tam thanamabhirocayim. ","tha-ap534:9.1":"Sasavakam tam vimalam, ","tha-ap534:9.2":"nimantetva tathagatam; ","tha-ap534:9.3":"Sattaham bhojayitvana, ","tha-ap534:9.4":"dussehacchadayim tada. ","tha-ap534:10.1":"Nipacca sirasa tassa, ","tha-ap534:10.2":"anantagunasagare; ","tha-ap534:10.3":"Nimuggo pitisampunno, ","tha-ap534:10.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap534:11.1":"‘Yo so taya santhavito, ","tha-ap534:11.2":"ito sattamake muni; ","tha-ap534:11.3":"Bhikkhu saddhavatam aggo, ","tha-ap534:11.4":"tadiso homaham mune’. ","tha-ap534:12.1":"Evam vutte, mahaviro, ","tha-ap534:12.2":"anavaranadassano; ","tha-ap534:12.3":"Imam vakyam udiresi, ","tha-ap534:12.4":"parisaya mahamuni. ","tha-ap534:13.1":"‘Passathetam manavakam, ","tha-ap534:13.2":"pitamatthanivasanam; ","tha-ap534:13.3":"Hemayannopacitangam, ","tha-ap534:13.4":"jananettamanoharam. ","tha-ap534:14.1":"Eso anagataddhane, ","tha-ap534:14.2":"gotamassa mahesino; ","tha-ap534:14.3":"Aggo saddhadhimuttanam, ","tha-ap534:14.4":"savakoyam bhavissati. ","tha-ap534:15.1":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap534:15.2":"sabbasantapavajjito; ","tha-ap534:15.3":"Sabbabhogaparibyulho, ","tha-ap534:15.4":"sukhito samsarissati. ","tha-ap534:16.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap534:16.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap534:16.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap534:16.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap534:17.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap534:17.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap534:17.3":"Vakkali nama namena, ","tha-ap534:17.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap534:18.1":"Tena kammavisesena, ","tha-ap534:18.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap534:18.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap534:18.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap534:19.1":"Sabbattha sukhito hutva, ","tha-ap534:19.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","tha-ap534:19.3":"Savatthiyam pure jato, ","tha-ap534:19.4":"kule annatare aham. ","tha-ap534:20.1":"Nonitasukhumalam mam, ","tha-ap534:20.2":"jatapallavakomalam; ","tha-ap534:20.3":"Mandam uttanasayanam, ","tha-ap534:20.4":"pisacibhayatajjita. ","tha-ap534:21.1":"Padamule mahesissa, ","tha-ap534:21.2":"sayesum dinamanasa; ","tha-ap534:21.3":"‘Imam dadama te natha, ","tha-ap534:21.4":"saranam hohi nayaka’. ","tha-ap534:22.1":"Tada patiggahi so mam, ","tha-ap534:22.2":"bhitanam sarano muni; ","tha-ap534:22.3":"Jalina cakkankitena, ","tha-ap534:22.4":"mudukomalapanina. ","tha-ap534:23.1":"Tada pabhuti tenaham, ","tha-ap534:23.2":"arakkheyyena rakkhito; ","tha-ap534:23.3":"Sabbaveravinimutto, ","tha-ap534:23.4":"sukhena parivuddhito. ","tha-ap534:24.1":"Sugatena vina bhuto, ","tha-ap534:24.2":"ukkanthami muhuttakam; ","tha-ap534:24.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap534:24.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap534:25.1":"Sabbaparamisambhutam, ","tha-ap534:25.2":"nilakkhinayanam varam; ","tha-ap534:25.3":"Rupam sabbasubhakinnam, ","tha-ap534:25.4":"atitto viharamaham. ","tha-ap534:26.1":"Buddharuparatim natva, ","tha-ap534:26.2":"tada ovadi mam jino; ","tha-ap534:26.3":"‘Alam vakkali kim rupe, ","tha-ap534:26.4":"ramase balanandite. ","tha-ap534:27.1":"Yo hi passati saddhammam, ","tha-ap534:27.2":"so mam passati pandito; ","tha-ap534:27.3":"Apassamano saddhammam, ","tha-ap534:27.4":"mam passampi na passati. ","tha-ap534:28.1":"Anantadinavo kayo, ","tha-ap534:28.2":"visarukkhasamupamo; ","tha-ap534:28.3":"Avaso sabbaroganam, ","tha-ap534:28.4":"punjo dukkhassa kevalo. ","tha-ap534:29.1":"Nibbindiya tato rupe, ","tha-ap534:29.2":"khandhanam udayabbayam; ","tha-ap534:29.3":"Passa upakkilesanam, ","tha-ap534:29.4":"sukhenantam gamissasi’. ","tha-ap534:30.1":"Evam tenanusitthoham, ","tha-ap534:30.2":"nayakena hitesina; ","tha-ap534:30.3":"Gijjhakutam samaruyha, ","tha-ap534:30.4":"jhayami girikandare. ","tha-ap534:31.1":"Thito pabbatapadamhi, ","tha-ap534:31.2":"assasayi mahamuni; ","tha-ap534:31.3":"Vakkaliti jino vacam, ","tha-ap534:31.4":"tam sutva mudito aham. ","tha-ap534:32.1":"Pakkhandim selapabbhare, ","tha-ap534:32.2":"anekasataporise; ","tha-ap534:32.3":"Tada buddhanubhavena, ","tha-ap534:32.4":"sukheneva mahim gato. ","tha-ap534:33.1":"Punopi dhammam deseti, ","tha-ap534:33.2":"khandhanam udayabbayam; ","tha-ap534:33.3":"Tamaham dhammamannaya, ","tha-ap534:33.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap534:34.1":"Sumahaparisamajjhe, ","tha-ap534:34.2":"tada mam caranantago; ","tha-ap534:34.3":"Aggam saddhadhimuttanam, ","tha-ap534:34.4":"pannapesi mahamati. ","tha-ap534:35.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap534:35.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap534:35.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap534:35.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap534:36.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap534:36.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap534:36.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap534:37.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap534:37.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap534:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap534:38.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap534:38.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap534:38.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap534:39.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vakkalitthero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap534:40.1":"Vakkalittherassapadanam dutiyam. "}